    "originContent": "In this project, all the experiments are conducted using [LMMs-Eval](https://github.com/EvolvingLMMs-Lab/lmms-eval). We provide FlashVID evaluation scripts in `scripts/`, including LLaVA-OneVision, LLaVA-Video, Qwen2.5-VL, and Qwen3-VL. You can run the scripts to reproduce our experimental results:",
