    "originContent": "📝**Note**: It is extremely easy to integrate FlashVID into LMMs-Eval by adding specific parameters in `__init__()` and wrapping the loaded model with the `flashvid()` function. (See `lmms_eval/models/simple/llava_onevision.py`)",
    "translatedContent": "📝**注意**: FlashVIDをLMMs-Evalに統合するのは非常に簡単で、`__init__()`に特定のパラメータを追加し、読み込んだモデルを`flashvid()`関数でラップするだけです。（詳細は`lmms_eval/models/simple/llava_onevision.py`を参照）"
